Privacy Policy 2024
Scrum Pokert uses Firebase Analytics and Crashlytics to see screen views and stack traces for crashes. This information in fully anonymous and cannot be traced back. This data is not linked to you.
Since Scrum Pokert does not collect any personal data or account information, you are in full control of your own data. Remove the app and your back-up files and all your journal data is gone forever.
For questions or inquiries about this privacy policy, please contact me at fsolleveld@outlook.com.
Updated January 18, 2024.